"
Description
--------------------

I am an abstract class whose responsibility is to validate a meta-model generated by a FMMetaModelBuilder.

In order to do that I know a builder and will do some validation on it.

I follow a Strategy design pattern and I will be used by FMMetaModelBuilder.

Public API and Key Messages
--------------------

- #validate 		Launch the validation of the metamodel builder.
 
Internal Representation and Key Implementation Points.
--------------------

    Instance Variables
	metaModelBuilder:		<aFMMataModelBuilder> 	The meta-model builder I need to validate.

"
Class {
	#name : #FMAbstractMetamodelValidator,
	#superclass : #Object,
	#instVars : [
		'metaModelBuilder'
	],
	#category : #'Fame-Core-Utilities'
}

{ #category : #'instance creation' }
FMAbstractMetamodelValidator class >> for: aPragmaProcessor [
	self new
		metaModelBuilder: aPragmaProcessor;
		validate
]

{ #category : #accessing }
FMAbstractMetamodelValidator >> metaModelBuilder [
	^ metaModelBuilder
]

{ #category : #accessing }
FMAbstractMetamodelValidator >> metaModelBuilder: anObject [
	metaModelBuilder := anObject
]

{ #category : #validation }
FMAbstractMetamodelValidator >> validate [
	self subclassResponsibility
]
